440
00:27:06,024 --> 00:27:07,659
You're still up.

441
00:27:09,294 --> 00:27:10,128
Yes.

442
00:27:12,130 --> 00:27:13,832
Are you having trouble sleeping too?

443
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:16,401
Yeah, a little.

444
00:27:21,806 --> 00:27:23,008
Would you…

445
00:27:24,709 --> 00:27:26,411
