446
00:27:27,379 --> 00:27:28,279
What?

447
00:27:37,055 --> 00:27:37,922
Sure.

448
00:28:03,348 --> 00:28:04,783
Oh, here.

449
00:28:07,886 --> 00:28:09,587
But Tae-o, you…

450
