454
00:28:24,769 --> 00:28:25,870
That's cool.

455
00:28:27,338 --> 00:28:31,543
I'm also good at withstanding the cold.

456
00:28:36,381 --> 00:28:38,049
Don't misunderstand.

457
00:28:38,116 --> 00:28:39,984
