459
00:28:48,793 --> 00:28:49,828
Thanks.

460
00:28:59,804 --> 00:29:00,939
It's pretty.

461
00:29:04,442 --> 00:29:05,276
Yes.

462
00:29:06,177 --> 00:29:08,246
It's very pretty.

463
00:29:40,712 --> 00:29:41,579
Sorry.

464
00:29:42,580 --> 00:29:46,251
