465
00:29:58,763 --> 00:29:59,831
You're right.

466
00:30:04,402 --> 00:30:05,837
It's prettier this way.

467
00:30:16,181 --> 00:30:17,115
You'll catch a cold.

468
00:30:25,790 --> 00:30:26,691
