472
00:30:40,972 --> 00:30:42,674
Oh, um…

473
00:30:43,408 --> 00:30:44,509
The star…

474
00:30:47,045 --> 00:30:48,346
Oh.

475
00:30:48,413 --> 00:30:50,281
-A shooting star?
-Yes.

476
00:30:51,115 --> 00:30:54,185
-Right.
-Wow, I wish I could've seen it.

477
00:30:55,887 --> 00:30:58,456
