478
00:30:59,023 --> 00:31:00,325
Yes, we do.

479
00:31:01,025 --> 00:31:02,894
Do you have a wish, Yuri?

480
00:31:02,961 --> 00:31:03,795
What?

481
00:31:03,862 --> 00:31:05,263
