00:38:12,556 --> 00:38:13,591
<i>How about me?</i>

540
00:38:14,992 --> 00:38:17,128
Do you like me?

541
00:38:40,918 --> 00:38:41,752
Hey…

542
00:38:45,389 --> 00:38:46,223
Hanaoka.

