I haven't told you how I feel at all.

594
00:43:08,118 --> 00:43:09,053
Yuri…

595
00:43:11,822 --> 00:43:13,324
To be honest, I…

596
00:43:17,728 --> 00:43:19,263
I actually…

597
00:43:33,444 --> 00:43:35,079
Yuri!

598
